                "invention-title": [
                    "Denitration process and device for flue gas in spodumene rotary kiln",
                    "一种锂辉石回转窑窑内烟气脱硝工艺及装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of spodumene rotary kiln flue gas treatment, and particularly relates to a process and a device for denitration of flue gas in a spodumene rotary kiln, and the process comprises the following steps: spraying ammonia water into a rotary kiln firing zone at a high temperature of 800-900 DEG C to carry out SNCR (selective non-catalytic reduction) reduction on NOx in the flue gas. The device is mounted on a kiln body of a firing zone of the rotary kiln at the temperature of 800-900 DEG C; the device consists of a metal hose (3.1), a quick rotating joint (3.2), an ammonia water main pipe (3.3), a protective castable (3.3. 1), a castable sleeve (3.3.2), an in-kiln pipeline bracket (3.3.3), an embedded sleeve (3.3.4), a detachable flange (3.3.5), an ammonia water branch pipe (3.4), an ammonia water spray head (3.5), a spray head shell (3.5. 1), an outlet wing (3.5. 2), a proportioning valve (3.6), a rotary kiln wheel belt (3.7), a wheel belt base plate (3.8), a rotary kiln riding wheel (3.9), a rotary kiln large gear (3.10), a large gear pulling plate (3.11) and a rotary kiln small gear (3.12). According to the process, an SCR catalysis module is not needed, the possibility of ammonia hydrogen sulfate and dust poisoning of the SCR catalysis module does not exist, compared with a traditional process, a rotary kiln flue gas heat supplementing device does not need to be arranged, and low carbon and energy saving are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于锂辉石回转窑烟气处理领域，特别涉及一种锂辉石回转窑窑内烟气脱硝工艺及装置，所述工艺为向回转窑烧成带内800‑900℃高温下喷入氨水对烟气中的NOx进行SNCR还原。所述装置安装位置在回转窑烧成带温度800～900℃区间窑体上，该装置由金属软管(3.1)、快速旋转接头(3.2)、氨水主管(3.3)、保护浇注料(3.3.1)、浇注料套管(3.3.2)、窑内管道支架(3.3.3)、预埋套管(3.3.4)、可拆卸法兰(3.3.5)、氨水支管(3.4)、氨水喷头(3.5)、喷头外壳(3.5.1)、出口凤翅(3.5.2)、比例调节阀(3.6)、回转窑轮带(3.7)、轮带垫板(3.8)、回转窑托轮(3.9)、回转窑大齿轮(3.10)、大齿轮拉板(3.11)、回转窑小齿轮(3.12)组成。此工艺不需SCR催化模块，不存在SCR催化模块硫酸氢氨及粉尘中毒的可能性，相较于传统工艺不需要设置回转窑烟气补热装置，低碳节能。"
                }
